  <div class="container">
    <section id="about">
      <h2>About Me</h2>
      <p>I’m a Mechanical Engineering student passionate about building and iterating. My experience spans CAD modeling, prototyping, and control systems for robotics, hybrid rocketry, and manufacturing tools. I thrive in hands-on environments and enjoy bringing ideas to life.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="projects">
      <h2>Featured Projects</h2>

      <div class="project">
        <h3>Servo Motion Demo | AutomationDirect</h3>
        <p>Designed and programmed a 4-axis stepper motor demo with live tuning and feedback. Involved CAD (SolidWorks), wiring stepper drivers, and troubleshooting noise/interference in signal wiring.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="project">
        <h3>Torch Igniter for Hybrid Rocket</h3>
        <p>Led early design efforts for a vortex-flow pancake torch igniter using COTS propane solenoids. Created flow simulations and conducted material/thermal analysis for sustained combustion initiation.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="project">
        <h3>Egg Peeler Design | ME 2110</h3>
        <p>Worked on a suction-based gripper system and function trees to prototype an automated boiled egg peeler. Used morphological charts and House of Quality matrices to guide trade-offs.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="experience">
      <h2>Experience</h2>

      <div class="experience">
        <h3>GT Propulsive Landers (Hybrid Rocket Team)</h3>
        <p>Member turned design lead for torch igniter. Learned quickly from scratch and contributed to mass flow and SEI research across design iterations. Jan 2025–Present.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="experience">
        <h3>GT Qurbani | Dance Team</h3>
        <p>Choreographer and captain. Designed 8-segment narrative production based on Poe’s “The Tell-Tale Heart,” incorporating fusion dance and stage direction. Aug 2023–Present.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

